{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"59017-olongbo-igbo-olongbo-igbo","title":"Wild cat! Wild cat!","description":"Se alabapade orisirisi olongbo igbo ti orile ede india.","language":"Yoruba","langCode":"yo","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["kehinde ademabayoje"],"illustrators":["Rohan Chakravarty"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/59017-olongbo-igbo-olongbo-igbo"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722383/size3/b67b65b0b4e07eecc3cd0aa184e1548c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722383/size6/b67b65b0b4e07eecc3cd0aa184e1548c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48623/size6/8c837e2790a2a776373a80fa987f0cf9.jpg","text":"Awon olongbo igbo kan ni ila.\nBi Ekun!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48624/size6/6ea91ca34bdbfc039fb6fdb69747f06c.jpg","text":"Awon Olongbo igbo kan ni irun ni orun.\nBi ekun!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48625/size6/98d89dc02165b900a45427fc94e73369.jpg","text":"Awon Olongbo igbo kan ni amin.\nBi Amotekun ati Amotekun ebi olongbo!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48626/size6/61f26c636cfb7774c734cb0201b21434.jpg","text":"Awon Olongbo igbo kan dara ni ibi ka pon igi.\nBi amotekun alawo resuresu ati olongbo alawo kalankini!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48627/size6/380edf3b9b22e6a29483061b0daaa2d1.jpg","text":"Awon olongbo igbo kan ngbe loke apata.\nBi amotekun ni agbegbe oniyinyin ati olongbo inu papa!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48628/size6/abcf82b334b1c3312e9c154b53c74755.jpg","text":"Awon olongbo igbo kan ngbe ni asale.\nBi olongbo inu asale!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48629/size6/e155294059bc64e40c3d85db7e1dc8c6.jpg","text":"Awon olongbo igbo kan ni irun pupo ni eti won.\nGege bi oniruuru awon olongbo!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48630/size6/66f9b62c88bc008a4d7fea2df3f28763.jpg","text":"Awon olongbo igbo kan feran lati maa pa eja.\nGege bi ebi olongbo kan!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48632/size6/d18d79f2ff91aebfa45ae8ef2cc6f0cd.jpg","text":"Awon olongbo igbo kan wa ti won kere ju lagbaye.\nBi olongbo alawo pupa lara!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48633/size6/5eeceb3f40b3e6a2e1c14ef23faec0a4.jpg","text":"Awon olongbo igbo kan dabi olongbo ile.\nBi olongbo aginju ati olongbo alawo didan!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48634/size6/7c01994016872d0d4908eccc906da432.jpg","text":"Sugbon gbogbo won olongbo igbo ni won!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":140}}